OL,3,CWho is standing for election in the
OL,4,CMidlands in 2024?
OL,6,FFor the first time, the election of
OL,7,FWest Midlands Mayor will take place
OL,8,Fusing the First Past the Post system,
OL,9,Fthe same as in a general election. It
OL,10,Fmeans the candidate with the highest
OL,11,Fnumber of votes wins.
OL,13,FWhich candidates are standing for
OL,14,FPolice & Crime Commissioner?
OL,16,FThe deadline for candidates to confirm
OL,17,Ftheir candidacy is the 5 April.
